reviews.text: Semi-all you can eat chicken pot and hotpot dinner.  You can enjoy hotpot with various soup base choices after unlimited fry chicken pot. The seafood and beef that included are fresh and tasty.

All you can eat buffet of chicken pot + regular hotpot, the set comes with one order of seafood and beef, need to pay for additional orders. But the above should be able to fill up your stomach already.  Extra funny waiter. The set ends with a home made milk pudding, which is quite delicious by itself.

Delicious chicken hotpot with reasonable prices! Unlimited chicken refill, unlimited hot pot ingredients (except premium seafood and beef) refill and unlimited non-alcoholic drinks makes this a very worth it place to eat! Good service too, they encourage us to order more and hello clear out our plates quite often!
One of the best chicken hotpot I had. Ultra tender!
Very yummy Num spicy Chicken pot as a starter, great hot pot and fresh seafood in good price and nice service!
